org.jhove2.persist
Interface SourceAccessor

All Known Implementing Classes:
BerkeleyDbSourceAccessor, InMemorySourceAccessor
public interface SourceAccessor

Interface to manage persistence of Source objects, and accessors and mutators for member fields that themselves are persisted objects

Author:
smorrissey
